  <brief_title>The Effect Of Probiotics On Bowel Function Restoration After Ileostomy Closure In Patients With Rectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect Of Probiotics From Kimchi (CJLP243) On Bowel Function Restoration After Ileostomy Closure In Patients With Rectal Cancer: A Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
